summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of lands and other property and property rights and privileges in King County for transmission system right of way, as provided for by Ordinance No. 43548, being Cause No. 159852 in the Superior Court of King County, Washington, in so far as the same affects certain of the property therein described; and appropriating money to pay all taxable costs incurred by the parties to said condemnation suit whose property is dismissed by this ordinance.
